        <para>
            
        </para>
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para>
                    <emphasis role="bold">Constant</emphasis>
                </para>
                <para> A matrix of any type.</para>
                <para> The size of the matrix gives the size of the regular output port.</para>
                <para> The constant(i,j) value is the component(i,j) value of the output port.</para>
                <para> From this value the block inherits its data type.</para>
                <para> Properties : Type 'mat' of size [-1,-2].</para>
            </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
    </refsection>
